Mr Ong‚Äôs group paints a stark reminder to us not to mindlessly follow others‚Äô calls. Mr Ong told to sell all position and his entire cult followed  missing out on the swift gains of blue chips after the election was over. The correct thing to have done was to sell blue chips when the decline was noted  and buy after the first daily candle (of strength) has formed.
